**Physics System:**
```javascript
for each particle:
  // Spring back to home position
  force += (home - position) * springK;

  // Neighbor repulsion
  for each neighbor within radius:
    force += repel(neighbor);

  // Mouse interaction
  force += mouseForce(mousePos, position);

  // Apply with damping
  velocity = velocity * damping + force * dt;
  position += velocity * dt;

  // Sleep optimization
